description: GeraNetwork: Table containing metadata and identifiers for Ericsson-specific GERAN (GSM/EDGE Radio Access Network) network elements.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp of data record), Area_Name (geographic area), CellId (unique identifier for the cell site), Id2 (duplicate of CellId), Id3 (likely a redundant identifier, always '1'), vsDataType (data type identifier, always 'vsDataGeraNetwork'), vsDataFormatVersion (data format version, always 'EricssonSpecificAttributes'), userLabel (unused label field), geraNetworkId (unique identifier for the GERAN network element, appears to always be '1').
